edium in fp32 exceeds the 8 GB reference\n714\tGPU. Precision therefore differs with size. To keep the two\n715\tapart, we re-run small-music in both fp32 and fp16 (Section\n716\tIV-B0a). The two dose–responses coincide (r=1.00), which\n717\tisolates the medium–small differences as scale rather than\n718\tprecision. Per-point significance is assessed with a two-sided\n719\tWilcoxon signed-rank test on the n=36 paired deltas, Holmcorrected across the five axes.\n720\t\n721\t\fTABLE III\n722\tD ENSE - WINDOW MULTI - ORACLE STEERING ( SMALL - MUSIC , FP 32), EACH\n723\tAXIS AT ITS WAV 2 TASTE - BEST LAYER . SWEET (L16) IS SHOWN ACROSS\n724\tTHE FULL α SWEEP ; THE INTENSE TASTES (L19) AT α=0.1 VS . 0.15. I N\n725\tEACH BLOCK THE TARGET (∆ W 2 T ) AND THE INDEPENDENT CLAP CHECK\n726\tRISE TOGETHER ONLY AT LOW α ( THE GENUINE WINDOW ); PAST IT CLAP\n727\tFLIPS NEGATIVE ( BOLD ) AND FAD JUMPS WHILE WAV 2 TASTE KEEPS\n728\tCLIMBING – METRIC - GAMING . SALTY BARELY MOVES CLAP EVEN WHEN\n729\tCLEAN ; SPICY IS MARGINAL .\n730\t\n731\t∆w2t\n732\t\n733\t∆CLAP\n734\t\n735\tFAD\n736\t\n737\tdrift\n738\t\n739\tsweet (L16): full sweep\n740\tsweet\n741\t0.1\n742\t+0.075\n743\t0.15 +0.097\n744\t0.2\n745\t+0.104\n746\t0.3\n747\t+0.119\n748\t0.5\n749\t+0.098\n750\t0.7\n751\t+0.056\n752\t1.0\n753\t−0.025\n754\t\n755\t+1.05\n756\t+1.43\n757\t+1.83\n758\t+2.11\n759\t+0.82\n760\t−1.16\n761\t−3.88\n762\t\n763\t73\n764\t144\n765\t274\n766\t515\n767\t777\n768\t933\n769\t1257\n770\t\n771\t0.11\n772\t0.16\n773\t0.25\n774\t0.39\n775\t0.52\n776\t0.57\n777\t0.72\n778\t\n779\tintense (L19): genuine at α=0.1\n780\tsour\n781\t0.1\n782\t+0.419\n783\t+1.77\n784\t0.15 +0.522\n785\t−0.63\n786\tbitter\n787\t0.1\n788\t+0.314\n789\t+1.66\n790\t0.15 +0.360\n791\t−1.15\n792\tsalty\n793\t0.1\n794\t+0.209\n795\t+0.32\n796\t0.15 +0.191\n797\t−0.98\n798\tspicy\n799\t0.1\n800\t+0.192\n801\t−0.18\n802\t0.15 +0.267\n803\t+0.25\n804\t\n805\t561\n806\t985\n807\t836\n808\t1222\n809\t576\n810\t885\n811\t301\n812\t574\n81